OL,3,CCrafter turns widower wife's
OL,4,Cunfinished knitting projects into gifts
OL,6,FA community crafter in Morecambe has
OL,7,Fturned the wife of a widowers knitting
OL,8,Fprojects into gifts for future
OL,9,Fgenerations.
OL,11,FJohn Heaton and his wife Sandra had
OL,12,Fbeen married for more than 50 years,
OL,13,Fbut on September 8th last year, she
OL,14,Fpassed away.
OL,16,FSandra left behind a large amount of
OL,17,Fknitting materials and projects -
OL,18,Fincluding a baby cardigan she had
OL,19,Fstarted.
