OL,3,CCrafter turns widower wife's
OL,4,Cunfinished knitting projects into gifts
OL,6,FA month later while searching online,
OL,7,FJohn came across the charity called
OL,8,FLoose Ends.
OL,10,FThey finish projects for people as
OL,11,Fwell as those whose loved ones have
OL,12,Fpassed away leaving something
OL,13,Fincomplete.
OL,15,FThe charity put him in touch with Pam,
OL,16,Fwho carefully picked up where Sandra
OL,17,Fhad left off.
OL,19,FPam Reiach, a volunteer finisher said:
OL,20,F"I didn't realise the emotion and the
OL,21,Finvolvement that you get with it.
