OL,3,CCrafter turns widower wife's
OL,4,Cunfinished knitting projects into gifts
OL,6,F"Although it is a small project, it
OL,7,Fwas a responsibility to finish it,
OL,8,Ffinish it properly, finish it well."
OL,10,FFor John, Pam's work and dedication
OL,11,Fhas provided some comfort in what has
OL,12,Fbeen a difficult year.
OL,14,FHe said: "It has helped me with my
OL,15,Fgrief knowing that Sandra's baby
OL,16,Fjacket has been finished by Pam,
OL,17,Fthat's really comforted me.
