OL,3,CCrafter turns widower wife's
OL,4,Cunfinished knitting projects into gifts
OL,6,F"I would like to give that to my
OL,7,Fgranddaughter as and when she grows up
OL,8,Fand has children and they can be
OL,9,Fpassed on, if they want to keep it for
OL,10,Fher children."
OL,12,FThe pair have now developed a
OL,13,Ffriendship and John has now gifted all
OL,14,Fof Sandra's wool and knitting
OL,15,Fmaterials to Pam.
OL,17,FIn the collection, Pam also found a
OL,18,Fhalf finished teddy bear which she
OL,19,Fcompleted and handed back to John as a
OL,20,Ftreasure.
