OL,3,CCrafter turns widower wife's
OL,4,Cunfinished knitting projects into gifts
OL,6,FPam now uses Sandra's materials to
OL,7,Fmake knitted items for babies in the
OL,8,Fneonatal intensive care unit at
OL,9,FLancaster Hospital.
OL,11,FWhen John found out he said he was
OL,12,F"delighted" and has even joined Pam to
OL,13,Fdrop off the items at the hospital.
OL,15,FJohn said his late wife Sandra would
OL,16,Fbe 'over the moon' to know her wool
OL,17,Fhas been put to such 'wonderful and
OL,18,Fhelpful use'.
